by keradus at 2014-10-28T20:13:17Z

What do you think @marcaube ?
I can't figure it out why it is needed to check prev token.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by marcaube at 2014-10-30T17:14:53Z

@keradus It was needed for parameters on multiple lines like

```php
$var = func(
    $foo,
    $bar,
    [1, 2, 3]
);
```

It may no longer be needed after your refactoring.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

