by marcaube at 2014-10-30T17:24:48Z

There was [one](https://github.com/fabpot/PHP-CS-Fixer/blob/master/Symfony/CS/Tests/Fixer/PSR2/ParenthesisFixerTest.php#L29) but it was not updated with the code.

The fixer now only check control structures, the test should be updated to reflect that.

